		<title>[TLoaG...] on Healthcare: Health Insurance (part 2)</title>
		<link>http://androw.is/blog/tloag-on-healthcare-health-insurance-part-2</link>
		<comments>http://androw.is/blog/tloag-on-healthcare-health-insurance-part-2#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 25 Jan 2010 01:25:32 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Andrew AbuMoussa</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Rants]]></category>
